### Get Category Roots
# Fetches the root level categories for marketplace navigation.
GET {{host}}/api/ads/categories?depth=1
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Category Roots with depth 2
# Fetches the root level categories and their immediate children.
GET {{host}}/api/ads/categories?depth=2
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Category Children
# Fetches the subcategories of a given category to allow deeper traversal.
# Replace {categoryId} with an actual ID from the roots request.
GET {{host}}/api/ads/categories/1/children?depth=1
Accept-Language: en-US

### Get Category Children with depth 2
# Fetches the subcategories and their own subcategories.
GET {{host}}/api/ads/categories/1/children?depth=2
Accept-Language: en-US

### Get Category Suggestions
# Returns a list of category leaf nodes matching the query, including full breadcrumb paths.
GET {{host}}/api/ads/categories/suggestions?p=electr
Accept-Language: en-US
